snippet.title: MiniLife: Tournament - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
MiniLife: Tournament is a cooperative real-time strategy game with never-ending 5x5 PvP battles.

Collect resources, develop your village, and go into battle riding siege llamas and combat barrel-walkers. Every team member and every decision makes a difference here!
